name: This is not an NFT
description:
A longtime art collector with no interest in the NFT craze was worried that they were missing out on my works in the NFT space. Trying to convince the collector to create a wallet was futile, So i created a hand drawn NFT that they could attach to their laptop with wire and then flexx hard with that 1/1 ! The collector took a photo of it after loading it up on their laptop. I took a photo of their photo and swapped it on HEN ! There has to be an easier way to make an NFT.
Created by Nite Owl, 2021. 
1238 x 1238 pixel, 300 dpi png file.
